STEP 4: LISTING ka correct logic
Goal

Admin ko:

Website bookings bhi dikhni chahiye

Admin-created bookings bhi

Same super admin ke andar ki sab

Correct WHERE condition (conceptually)
booking.parentAdminId IN (
  all admins where superAdminId = currentSuperAdminId
)
OR
booking.parentAdminId IS NULL (website bookings)


